LINE.Text: The National Park Service and Clemson University teamed up with the NOAA Marine
Debris Program to collect and analyze beach sediments to assess the abundance and
distribution of microplastics and microfibers on U.S. National Park beaches. This was a
'snapshot' study and results are based on one sampling point in time.
